{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Humanoid abominations are violently taking over a colony on a faraway planet. While waiting for the evacuation vessels to arrive, help your team rescue as many survivors as you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802670/extras/ConvertedCombatGif.gif?t=1729156530\" />\u2022Horde combat: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Position yourself strategically, and take out multiple enemies with each attack to prevent being overwhelmed and cornered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802670/extras/SwordDescriptionSet.png?t=1729156530\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802670/extras/CovnertedSwordTypes2.gif?t=1729156530\" />\u2022Weapon customization: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can\u00a0perform four different attacks, which are determined by the way you build your sword.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802670/extras/NewOrganUpgradeDescription.png?t=1729156530\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802670/extras/HeartSetNew.png?t=1729156530\" />\u2022Body customization: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Replace body parts with cybernetic implants and enhanced lab-grown organs to gain special abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802670/extras/AbominationMerge.gif?t=1729156530\" />\u2022Dynamic enemies: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The commonly-encountered base breeds of abominations have set behaviors you can study, but as the game progresses, they gain the ability to merge with one another, birthing horrifying monsters with inherited and enhanced strengths.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Fast and efficient","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1802670/090780e66f1e742b5bb3a2686ffcc7b90eec90c3.jpg"},{"name":"That's a big sword","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1802670/4ac8bcefccbb0642a08e917bccb68c75490a6d5e.jpg"},{"name":"Sky's is the limit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1802670/ad899563a7428fd126fd603f5a287a7f025b4b01.jpg"},{"name":"Dizziness","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1802670/77a43d39b3c6c1d33fff73f2ea92958a4c917d3f.jpg"},{"name":"Classic choice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1802670/275dd8af9894a604182d06883bc2436347f99603.jpg"},{"name":"Whoosh","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1802670/ea7d042526dbee0e7220bef0539401c8639f819f.jpg"},{"name":"Like grinding cheese","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1802670/fd6ba5f355eea5cc8fe57be74874782dcb12641d.jpg"},{"name":"Poke poke poke","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1802670/1d1b0a49f557ab15697af09f96632d740003c143.jpg"},{"name":"More than one way to skin an abomination","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1802670/3da0241f6f9b7da286b84db076317ac26b0a7ada.jpg"},{"name":"Chop chop chop","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1802670/443356c03b4104243741870151e7b9a905c1ec5e.jpg"}],"total":31},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1802670/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729156530","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.co